<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css'/>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="javascripts/vote.js"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Livvic:400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<div id="content" class="container">
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <hr>
    <div id="poster-container" class="poster d-none">
        <img id="poster-preview" src="">
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center">
        <h2 id="quote">
            Laddar...
        </h2>



        <p>Ett av de åtta riksdagspartierna har skrivit detta på sin valaffisch.<br>Håller du med, står du bakom påståendet eller är detta något du vill ha?</p>

        <p>
            <button id="yes" class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block answer-btn" onclick="vote(1)" disabled>Ja</button>
            <button id="yes" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg btn-block answer-btn" onclick="vote(0)" disabled>Hoppa över</button>
            <button id="yes" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg btn-block answer-btn" onclick="vote(-1)" disabled>Nej</button>
            <button id="yes" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block res-btn d-none" onclick="openResult()">Se resultat</button>
        </p>
        <u><i class="cursor-pointer text-secondary" onclick="show()">Visa affisch</i></u>

        <i id="remaining" class="text-secondary">0/0</i>

    </div>
</div>


<script>

</script>
</body>
</html>
